document_data.name: Yalanilue
document_data.mainbody: '''Yalanilue''' was a maid of house [[Alastrarra]] of [[Cormanthyr]] in the 3{{rd}} century [[DR]].
document_data.History: In {{yearlink|241}}, she was dancing off on a corner of the house. According to the ''[[selu'kiira]]'' of [[Iymbryl Alastrarra]], he'd seen her dance like that once, except unclad.
